00:00:36.602 --> 00:00:39.205
Russia lost 50 million people

00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:41.807
and helped us win the war.

00:00:41.807 --> 00:00:43.743
I was saying to myself

00:00:43.743 --> 00:00:44.877
the other day, you know,

00:00:44.877 --> 00:00:46.513
Russia really helped us.

00:00:46.513 --> 00:00:49.314
I'm not pro-Russia, pro-anybody.

00:00:49.314 --> 00:00:50.749
-I'm not pro-anybody.

00:00:50.749 --> 00:00:52.352
It would have been
much more honest

00:00:52.352 --> 00:00:54.921
if Trump said that with his hand
on the Bible.

00:00:54.921 --> 00:00:56.822
[ As Trump ]
I'm not pro-anybody.

00:00:56.822 --> 00:01:00.560
