interferes in our elections,

00:01:15.441 --> 00:01:16.876
kills journalists
and dissidents,

00:01:16.876 --> 00:01:19.978
uses nerve gas on foreign soil,
and invades its neighbors.

00:01:19.978 --> 00:01:23.516
Yet, Trump, who has repeatedly
cast himself as a fighter

00:01:23.516 --> 00:01:26.619
and counter puncher, wouldn't
each use the word "adversary"

00:01:26.619 --> 00:01:27.820
to describe Russia.

00:01:27.820 --> 00:01:30.089
-Are they our chief adversary,
