00:01:33.859 --> 00:01:35.161
as you know, than China,

00:01:35.161 --> 00:01:37.463
and I don't want to even use
the word "adversary."

00:01:37.463 --> 00:01:39.432
We can all work together.
We can do great.

00:01:39.432 --> 00:01:41.634
Everybody can do well,
and we can live in peace.

00:01:41.634 --> 00:01:43.603
-This guy will wake up
at 5:00 a.m.

00:01:43.603 --> 00:01:46.272
to tweet nasty things about
everyone from Snoop Dogg

00:01:46.272 --> 00:01:48.174
to Meryl Streep,
but when it comes to Russia,

00:01:48.174 --> 00:01:51.043
