Ringo Starr.

00:01:51.043 --> 00:01:53.012
[ As Ringo ]
We can all live together as one,

00:01:53.012 --> 00:01:55.014
peace and love, peace and love,

00:01:55.014 --> 00:01:58.551
no collusion, no collusion,
peace and love.

00:01:58.551 --> 00:02:02.155
[ Cheers and applause ]

