00:02:04.056 --> 00:02:05.424
what he's saying sounds great.

00:02:05.424 --> 00:02:07.493
Of course it would be ideal
if we could be at peace

00:02:07.493 --> 00:02:08.561
with our adversaries.

00:02:08.561 --> 00:02:09.928
